\h Jut
\toc3 JU
\toc2 Jut
\toc1 Jut Osirizir Ak…®nafarim
\mt1 Jut Osirizir Ak…®nafarim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Jut
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n akaba, da mong 2 Pitan akaba ko magh ghu. A God…®n gumazamizibav k…®masa, eght…® me Akar Aghuim…®n apanibar akaba baragh dar g…®n mangan kogham. Ak…®nafarir kam (ves 3) kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE God…®n gumazamiziba, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazir vam…®ram e gan…®ngi. Eght…® gumazamiziba en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim batuegh…®va, akar igiatam ar…®ghan kogham.‚Äù
\c 1
\ms1 Ia uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba bagh gan
\b
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Matyu 13:55; Mak 6:3; Jon 17:11-12; 1 Pita 1:5\x*K…® Jut, k…® Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazim; egha k…® Jems…®n dozim. Ia God diazir gumazamiziba, k…® ia bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. God Afeziam bar ia gifonge, ez…® Krais Iesus uab…® ian gari.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 1 Pita 1:2; 2 Pita 1:2\x*Apangkuvim…®n arazim ko navir am…®rizim ko igharaz darazi gifongezir arazim bar ia giz…®fagh.
\s1 God…®n Akar Aghuim…®n apaniba, me Krais…®n adarazir aven ize
\r (2 Pita 2:1-18)
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Filipai 1:27; 1 Timoti 1:18; 6:12; 2 Timoti 1:13; Taitus 1:4\x*Nan namakar aghuiba, k…® faragha ingangarir God ua bar e inizir kam…®n, ak…®nafarim osirigha ia m…®k…®masa bar ifonge. Egha k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, k…® ak…®nafarir igharazim osiram. Ia uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba bagh bar gavgafigh. Egh ia God…®n akar aghuim…®n apanibar akaba batogh. E God…®n gumazamiziba, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazir vam…®ram e gan…®ngi. Eght…® gumazamiziba en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim batuegh…®va, akar igiatam ar…®ghan kogham. Bar puvat…®.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Galesia 2:4; Taitus 1:16; 2 Pita 2:1; 1 Jon 2:22\x*Gumazamizir maba muega Krais…®n adarazir aven ize. Fom…®ra fom…®ra God kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazamizir kamagh…®n amiba me an damazim…®n m…®tivigh ovengam. Me ak…®riba ragha God gasi. Egha me God…®n apangkuvim…®n akabagh iragha dagh amima, da afiar arazibar akabar m…®n oto. Gumazamizir kaba ak…®rim ragha Atrivir vam…®ran kam gasara. An en Ekiam Krais Iesus.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:51; D…®boboniba 14:29-30; Onger Akaba 106:26; 1 Korin 10:5; 10:9; Hibru 3:17-19; 2 Pita 1:12\x*Ia bizir kabagh fogha g…®fa, ez…® k…® ua ian n…®ghn…®ziba fasa. Ia fo, Ekiam fom…®ra Isip…®n uan gumazamizibar akuraz…®ma me Isip ataki. Egha a g…®n gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®zibagh as…®ghas…®ki.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Grigh…®n ak…®nafarir av…®rir fom…®ra itiba, me ziar kam, ‚ÄúEkiam,‚Äù osirizir puvat…®. Me ziar kam, ‚ÄúIesus,‚Äù an osiri.\f*
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Jon 8:44; 2 Pita 2:4; 2:9; Akar Mogomem 20:10\x*Ia ensel…®n kurar maba, ia dagh n…®ghn…®gh. God me gan…®ngizir ingangariba me dar amuan aghua. Egha me uan danganiba ataki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ekiam zurara ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiamin senbar me ike. Egha me isa kalabuziar danganir bar m…®tarmangiz…®m…®n me ar…®ki. Ez…® me Kotiam Damuamin Dughiar Ekiam m…®zuai.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Jenesis 19:1-24; 2 Pita 2:6; 2:10\x*Kamagh…®ra, fom…®ra Sodom ko Gomoran gumaziba ko nguibar ekiar aning…®n borogh…®ra itibar gumaziba, me uaghan enselba amizir arazim…®n m…®rara ami. Me uari isa arazir kurabagh an…®ga, egha me arazir bar kurar gumaziba ko gumaziba uari isava akuibagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God me isa avir zurara isia mamagh…®ra itim…®n, me akuniz…®, me ivezir kuram ini. Bizir otivizir kaba, ia dagh n…®ghn…®gh…®va arazir kurabar g…®n mangan kogham.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:28; 2 Pita 2:10\x*Kamagh…®ra gumazamizir kaba ian n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa me arazir kurar kabar g…®nt…®si. Me irebar kurabar garima da men n…®ghn…®ziba fema me arazir bar kurar m…®z…®r…®zibar uan m…®karzibagh ami. Me Ekiam…®n akaba barazir puvat…®, egha God…®n Nguibam…®n itir ensel…®n ekiaba uaghan akar kurabar me m…®gei.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt God…®n Araziba 34:6; Daniel 10:13; 10:21; 12:1; Sekaraia 3:2; 2 Pita 2:11-12\x*Ez…® ensel…®n aghuiba, akar kurabar gumazir men apanibagh amibav geir puvat…®. Dughiar kam…®n, enselbar faragha zuim Maikel, a Moses…®n kuam bagha Satan ko aning uaning adoghodogha Maikel akar kuratam Satan m…®kemezir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam uab…® n…®n atar n…® m…®kemeght…®ma n…® uan akam dukuagh.‚Äù
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Pita 2:12\x*Gumazamizir kaba bizibar m…®ngaribagh fozir puvat…®, me puram akar kurabav gei. Me mati as…®zir n…®ghn…®ziba puvat…®zibar m…®n iti. Egha me uan inivaf…®ziba ifongezir arazibar g…®n zui. Ez…® men arazir kabara me gas…®ghas…®si.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Jenesis 4:3-8; D…®boboniba 16:1-35; 22:1-35; 2 Pita 2:15; 1 Jon 3:12\x*Me bar ikuvigham! Me Kein aruiz…® mogh…®n arui. Me ivezim baghav…®ra n…®ghn…®si, egha Balam amiz…® mogh…®n ami. Egha me dag…®aba iniasa bar ikufi. Egha me Koran m…®n God…®n akabar g…®nt…®zir puvat…®, egha arazir kam bang…®n me bar ovegha ikuvigha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Esekiel 34:8; Matyu 15:13; 1 Korin 11:21; Efesus 4:14; 2 Pita 2:13; 2:17; Akar Mogomem 2:11; 20:14\x*Ia uarigh ifongezir isar dughiabar, gumazamizir kaba izava God…®n damazim…®n arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kurabagh ami. Me damasa aghums…®zir puvat…®, egha kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, e isar ekiam…®n iti. Egha me uarira uarigh n…®ghn…®si. Me mati amozim puvat…®zir ghuariabar m…®n, am…®nim dagh ivaima, da tintinibar zui. Egha me mati temem uan dughiam…®n ber puvat…®. Egha me mati temem m…®sigha g…®vaz…® gumaziba an povim asiaghat…®. Me gumazamizir bar ovengeziba.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Aisaia 57:20; Filipai 3:19; 2 Pita 2:17\x*Me mati ongarir f…®f…®zir ekiaba d…®p…®raghiri. Egha me arazir kurabar amuasa aghums…®zir puvat…®gha, mati ongarim d…®p…®ra izima an puvpuvir m…®z…®r…®ziba p…®n otivi mogh…®n men arazir kuraba azenim giri. Egha me mati m…®koveziba p…®n overiam…®n uan tuavibar g…®nt…®zir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God me bagha danganir m…®tarmer bar p…®ghatomezim at…®, eght…® me mang…® an ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Jenesis 5:18-24; God…®n Araziba 33:2; Daniel 7:10; Sekaraia 14:5; Matyu 25:31; 2 Tesalonika 1:7; Akar Mogomem 1:7\x*Enok, an Adam…®n ovavir borir namba 6, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n m…®n gumazir kabav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Ekiam…®n garima a uan tausen ensel…®n bar av…®rav…®rim ko izi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Onger Akaba 31:18; Malakai 3:13\x*A gumazamiziba bar men araziba tuis…®gham. Gumazamizir an g…®n zuir puvat…®ziba, a me damut…®, me bar uan arazir kurar me amizibar os…®mt…®ziba ateram. Gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiba, me ak…®rim ragha God gasa ghuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, akar bar kurar igharazir me God gamiziba bang…®n, God me damut…®, me bar ivezir kuram iniam.‚Äù
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Jems 2:1; 2:9; 2 Pita 2:10; 2:18\x*Gumazamizir kaba, me bativir biziba me da bagha naviba ikufi, egha me puv m…®gei. Me uan navibar arazir kurabar g…®n zui. Me pamtem…®n diava puv uan ziaba fe. Egha me gumazamiziba apezeperima me me ifongezir arazibar g…®n zui.
\s1 Ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim, gavgavim ian navibar an…®ng
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt 2 Pita 3:2\x*Nan namakar bar aghuiba, ia g…®n otivamin bizim g…®n…®ghn…®gh, en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n aposelba an gun m…®keme.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 1 Timoti 4:1; 2 Timoti 3:1; 2 Pita 2:1; 3:3\x*Me kamagh…®n ia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDughiar abuananabar, gumazamizir d…®bovibagh amiba otivam, egh me God…®n Arazibar aghuagh…®va uan inivaf…®ziba ifongezir arazibar g…®n mangam.‚Äù
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt 1 Korin 2:14-15; Hibru 10:25; Jems 3:15\x*Gumazamizir kaba Krais…®n adarazi ab…®si. Me nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n zui, ez…® God…®n Duam men itir puvat…®.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Rom 8:26; Efesus 6:18; Kolosi 2:7; 1 Tesalonika 5:11\x*Ez…® ia guiz…®n nan adarasi, ia dughiabar zurara uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n gavgavim uan navibar an…®ng. N…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam, God uab…® ia gan…®ngi. Ia God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n zurara God ko m…®k…®m.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Taitus 2:13; 2 Pita 3:12\x*God bar ia gifonge. Kamagh…®n, ia an borogh…®n ik…®t…® a zurara ia gifuegham. Ia zurara e uan Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n m…®zuam, eght…® a uan apangkuvim azenim dat…®ght…®ma, ia ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarir zurara itim iniam.
\p 
\v 22 Ia, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim oteveziba, ia men apangkuf.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Amos 4:11; Sekaraia 3:2-5; Rom 11:14; 1 Korin 3:15; Akar Mogomem 3:4\x*Marazi avim…®n iti mogh…®n iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia zuam…®ram avim…®n me inigh. Ez…® marazi bar navir ghurim…®n arazibagh ami, egha me bar m…®ze, ez…® men korotiaba uaghan bar m…®ze. Eght…® dughiar ia men apangkuviba, ia God…®n atiating…®va uari bagh gan. Ia God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir bizir kaba bar dar saghon ik…®.
\s1 E God…®n ziam fam
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Rom 16:25; Efesus 3:20; Filipai 1:10; Kolosi 1:22; 2 Pita 3:14\x*God uab…® deraghv…®ra ian gant…® ia iran kogham. Eght…® a ia inigh mang…®t…® ia an nguibar aghuim…®n ikiam. Egh ia an damazim…®n arazir kuraba puvat…®gh, bar akuegham.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Rom 16:27; 1 Timoti 1:17; 2:3; 2 Pita 3:18\x*Kar God…®n vam…®ra, a en Akurvazir Gumazim, a Krais Iesus en Ekiam…®n ingangarim…®n, uam e ini. Eght…® e an ziam fam. A en atrivir faragha zuim…®n ikiava, egha gavgavir ekiam iti. Egh a biziba bar dar dapanim…®n iti. A dughiaba bar fom…®ra iza kamagh…®ra iti. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n a uaghan kamagh…®ra iti. Egh a g…®n uaghan kamagh…®ra ikiam. Bar guizbang…®ra.
